         "id": "introduction",
         "target": "",
         "page": "",
         "value_type": "",
         "html_value": "<p><hr /></p><p>Teaching goes beyond simply presenting information to be memorized. With the goal of supporting this mission, this page offers free educational games and applications.</p><p><b>The games can be updated at any time. <span id=\"family_common_sn\"></span></b></p>",
         "value": null,
         "date_time": null
      },
      {
